<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.4.10">
<l>uṭalāḻip piṟappuvī ṭuyirmutalā muṟṟumāyk</l>
<l>kaṭalāḻi nīrtōṟṟi yataṉuḷḷē kaṇvaḷaru</l>
<l>maṭalāḻi yammāṉaik kaṇṭakkā litucolli</l>
<l>viṭalāḻi maṭaneñcē viṉaiyōmoṉ ṟāmaḷavē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When you see the lord with the deadly discus,</l>
<l>who closes [his] eyes on him who appears in ring form in the sea,</l>
<l>as life begins with birth [and] ends in release, in the circle of bodies,</l>
	<l>speak this</l>
<l>[and] sink to be released, foolish heart. We carry karma as long as we are one [with it].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
